$ Oracle Enterprise Manager
@ OEM


{ OEM Cloud Control

  Cloud Control is web based

  Components of Cloud Control
    • Oracle Management Service (OMS) (A set of J2EE applications)
    • Oracle Management Agents (processes deployed on each monitored host)
    • Oracle Management Repository (basically an Oracle schema)

  → development/databases/Oracle/tools/RMAN is accessible from the Cloud Control. It's possible to define a *job schedule* and specify *job parameters*.


}
{ OEM Database Express 12

  Built into the database -> no special installation or management required.

  EM Express only has basic administration pages:
    • Database home page
    • Real-Time → development/databases/Oracle/SQL monitoring
    • ASH Analytics

}
